{"parentUuid":"c1634029-0c16-4650-8b1f-81aea09b8187","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_018NitjwDFqXj3MoHVtFMnUz","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\n```gitignore\n# Conversation logs (large, session-specific)\nprojects/**/*.jsonl\nprojects/**/subagents/\nprojects/**/tool-results/\n\n# File history (large, session-specific)\nfile-history/\n\n# Tasks (session-specific)\ntasks/\n\n# Shell snapshots\nshell-snapshots/\n\n# Cache\ncache/\npaste-cache/\nstats-cache.json\n\n# Credentials (NEVER sync)\n.credentials.json\nmcp-needs-auth-cache.json\n\n# Backups\nbackups/\n\n# Session files\nsessions/\nsession-states/\n\n# Lock files\n**/.lock\n**/.highwatermark\n\n# Plugins are git repos / auto-installed — don't nest repos\nplugins/\n```\n\n**What this syncs** (the valuable stuff):\n- `projects/*/memory/` — all your memories\n- `settings.json` — model, effort, plugin config\n- `plans/` — saved plans\n\n**What this excludes:**\n- Conversation logs (`.jsonl`) — huge, ephemeral\n- Credentials — must re-auth per machine\n- Plugins — auto-installed from marketplace config in `settings.json`, and they contain nested `.git` repos which cause problems\n- Session/task/cache data — ephemeral"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":226,"cache_read_input_tokens":47843,"output_tokens":301,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":226,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":3,"output_tokens":301,"cache_read_input_tokens":47843,"cache_creation_input_tokens":226,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":226},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CaA3m53bTEfc8wBfBT1u1","type":"assistant","uuid":"7dc553ed-461a-41be-8ab4-3755da960317","timestamp":"2026-